South African novelist Andre Brink on power-games with languages. Unwelcome guests inside our bodies, with American biologist Eugene Kaplan. And American-Iranian scholar Vali Nasr on the rise of the 'critical middle' in the Muslim world . Illustration by Emily Kasriel.